==English==

===Noun===
'''[[semelfactive]] [[aspect]]'''

#{{grammar}}: The '''semelfactive aspect''' refers to a subclass of [[perfective aspect|perfective]] verbs that denotes a [[momentary]] or punctiliar action (e.g., to [[sneeze]], to [[blink]]).

